title: Kevin Nealon
itunes:title: Kevin Nealon
description:
Kevin Nealon (SNL, Weeds, Happy Gilmore) and Whitney are real friends and on this pod they talk about Anthony Bourdain, Woody Allen, and eighty-thousand dollar storage units. Plus, Whitney debuts Emily's first and last stand up set and Benton tells us about his tax saga. Watch Kevin's web series Hiking With Kevin on YouTube.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
